sourcesContent: import { Container,makeStyles,Typography,Avatar,ImageList,ImageListItem,Link } from '@material-ui/core'; import { AvatarGroup } from '@material-ui/lab/'; import Calendar from 'react-calendar'; const useStyles = makeStyles((theme) => ({ container: { paddingTop: theme.spacing(10), }, title:{ fontSize:16, fontWeight: 500, color: "#555", }, link:{ marginRight: theme.spacing(2), color: "#555", fontSize: 16, }, })); export default function RightBar() { const classes = useStyles(); return ( Online friends Gallery Categories Sport Food Movies News ); }
